    <abstract>
      <t>   This document is a companion to RFC 7925 and defines TLS/DTLS 1.3
   profiles for Internet of Things devices.  It also updates RFC 7925
   with regards to the X.509 certificate profile and ciphersuite
   requirements.

	 </t>
